  "texts": [
    "We can efficiently uncover and address a wide range of user needs through detailed data analysis.",
    "We can look beyond the core functionalities and address broader aspects like scalability, availability, accessibility, security, and maintainability.",
    "For instance, scalability concerns are identified when user data indicates an increased load.",
    "Adjusting the scale of the software either too early or too late can lead to operational challenges.",
    "It is thus essential to effectively leverage the feedback loop mechanism to ensure that these adjustments are timely and align with the constantly developing requirements.We actively collect feedback from users in our APP development life cycle."
